snippet.title: Urusei Yatsura - Miss Tomobiki wo Sagase!
snippet.description:
Released by Yanoman, "The Search for Miss Tomobiki" is a Gameboy game from 1992. It's a maze game where the player controls Ataru and you wander through long corridors where you encounter other characters.

The audio drops out for awhile, but it picks back up later.

You can read more about Urusei Yatsura video games at:
http://www.furinkan.com/uy/odds/videogames.html
